message: I noticed an unusual time gap in some messages and images, but I truly didn’t think anything of it until about two weeks later. One night, I had a funny feeling and grabbed her tablet to do what I thought would be just another normal check. What I found to this day haunts my mind and makes my heart sink.

data.description: Dig into your children’s social media accounts, ask them questions, and tell them not to have “friends” they don’t actually know.
data.title: My Daughter Was Almost The Victim Of Human Sex Trafficking
